abstract: >-
  This repository provides public-safe facts, structured data (JSON-LD), prompt libraries,
  and guardrails to help search engines and large language models accurately describe
  Wind River Environmental (WRE) and its septic, grease trap, drain, and wastewater services.
  It is maintained by Perrill as an independent GEO/LLM reference and is not an official
  Wind River Environmental documentation or support site.

